{"tid":2178323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8.28民調結果 (54%離開:24%留任)","createTime":"2020-08-28T09:59:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T12:23:48.000Z","uid":189046,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"23dd536bb1f47a3edb7c67870845c89ea8636bdc","tid":2178323,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T09:59:59.000Z","msg":"【調查：逾半受訪市民支持全部民主派議員離開立法會】<br />\n<br />\n香港民意研究所發放「我們香港人意見群組調查」，調查有關民主派立法會議員應以哪種方式，處理是否接受延任第六屆立法會的問題，調查由本周一開始，截至本周三，以電郵訪問了17460位香港人，市民可選擇多一個選項，有逾半數市民支持民主派立法會議員全部離開。<br />\n<br />\n香港民意研究所經理戴捷輝表示，合計民主派和非民主派支持者的人數，54%的受訪者支持民主派議員全部離開，24%支持全部留任，而14%贊成個別議員自行決定，12%則贊成部分留任或離開，但由民主派集體決定。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/photos/a.723529797755079/3778325545608807/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2Fphotos%2Fa.723529797755079%2F3778325545608807%2F&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyFYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=9eac4a50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/photos/a.723529797755079/3778325545608807/</a>"},{"pid":"0ddc810d03503ec6f0b8e251813fb358b111cd77","tid":2178323,"uid":258770,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T10:03:50.000Z","msg":"泛民: 唔夠66%姐係民意唔想我地走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09fbec2f3c3c1d22d9edfc832f1ea8d25ffb9438","tid":2178323,"uid":173814,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T10:04:23.000Z","msg":"你個topic咁都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a2772a59b80f35d8f0d5ab4bbcc3c7b468c8faf","tid":2178323,"uid":41368,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T10:04:37.000Z","msg":"泛民今次要民意定要出糧呢？"},{"pid":"62ee15033462503d7206abeff9ab9d85007a40dd","tid":2178323,"uid":39365,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T10:05:39.000Z","msg":"根本泛民點樣都唔會走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e6